Class QVTOConfiguration

java.lang.Object

public class QVTOConfiguration
extends de.upb.m2m.quality.languages.AbstractLanguageConfiguration

A QVT-O-specific implementation of the AbstractLanguageConfiguration. Includes all information needed by the M2M Quality Metric Framework to measure QVT-O transformation metrics.

Version:
0.1
Author:
Sebastian Lehrig (lehrig@mail.upb.de)
